The paper discusses the Lovasz-Bregman divergence in the context of rank aggregation, order-based clustering, and web ranking. These topics are closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures (cs.DS), social networks (cs.SI), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
